import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom'
import Route from './components/Route'

import './styles/minireset.min.css'
import './styles/index.css'
import './styles/responsive.css'

  <React.StrictMode>
    <Route />
  </React.StrictMode>,
  document.getElementById('root')
)
